# Local SFX-authoring toolchain (rFXGen + its raylib build). Lives in
# tools/ so it never pollutes the system; never committed because it's
# huge + platform-specific. See gen_sfx.sh for the authoring pipeline.
# The .rfx parameter files (assets/sfx/rfx/) ARE committed — they're
# hand-authored source-of-truth; gen_sfx.sh bakes them to WAVs.
tools/